  {
    "speaker": "interviewee",
    "tag": "EA",
    "text": "Uh-- these are uh-- the five cousins. I am the one on the bottom right. I am about, oh, three or four years old. Must be around-- uh-- 1936. Uh-- next to me is my cousin Susan, who survived the Holocaust. Uh-- her sister Bella is behind me. She also survived. Uh-- the little boy is-- uh-- another cousin, [? Zenic ?]. He-- uh-- he was-- died during the Holocaust. And behind him is my cousin [? Gisella ?], his sister, who survived. She stayed with us during the-- uh-- German occupation. And he survived on-- uh-- Christian-- uh-- papers. [BACKGROUND NOISE]",
